snippet.title: Magic Trick - Steam Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Magic Trick on Steam!!! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1394320/Magic_Trick 

#MagicTrickGame is a skating adventure game about community! As the new WizKid in town, perform magic using rad skating combos, explore the whimsical city, and socialize with your wacky new neighbors who could use more magic in their lives! Play the beta here:  https://magictrick.itch.io/magic-trick

Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/MagicTrickGame
Check out our website: https://www.magictrickgame.com/
